Private car hit back of another car

If no injury or very minor like neck pain or whatever.:Take photos of the involved vehicles   general view showing which lane if possible with both cars and the damaged area along with your plate numbers if possible. Take photo of driver's IC (both sides) or note down. Move your vehicles aside properly if its obstructing traffic.  Then you can either -1. Private settlement with the other party  make sure you both agree to the compensation amount for damages  take out a piece of paper  write it out and both of you sign  get a witness if possible or video the signing of the agreement and properly keep that paper till the amount has been paid in case the other party wants to run so in court got evidence to go against him.2. Claim insurance  exchange both party's insurance information  NCD will be affected. Need to do within 24hrs  call your insurance company and explain what happened and give him the other party's particulars and vehicle number  he will do up the report for you. Then get ready to draw what happened if you got no in-car camera footage.If got serious injuries:Call 995 and 999 straight. Do not move the vehicles.
